(E_1 \backslash E_2) \cup (E_1 \cap E_2) = E_1
P(E_1 \backslash E_2) + P(E_1 \cap E_2) = P(E_1)
P(E_1 \backslash E_2) = P(E_1) - P(E_1 \cap E_2)
(E_1 \cap E_2) \cup (E_2 \backslash E_1) = E_2
 P(E_1 \cap E_2) + P(E_2 \backslash E_1) = P(E_2)
 P(E_2 \backslash E_1) = P(E_2) - P(E_1 \cap E_2)
